'''安娜·帕特里夏·柏廷·桑兹·索托拉·奥谢'''（{{lang-es|Ana Patricia Botín-Sanz de Sautuola O'Shea}}，[[大英帝國勳章|DBE]]，{{bd|1960年|10月4日|||catIdx=B}}）是一位西班牙银行家，自2014年以来一直担任[[桑坦德銀行|桑坦德銀行]]的执行主席。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-29149536|title=Santander appoints Ana Botin as chairwoman|work=BBC News|access-date=2020-08-06|archive-date=2018-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180701163341/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-29149536|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Ms Ana Botín-Sanz de Sautuola y O'Shea|url=https://www.santander.com/csgs/Satellite/CFWCSancomQP01/en_GB/Corporate/Investor-Relations/Ms-Ana-Botin-Sanz-de-Sautuola-y-OShea.html|website=www.santander.com|language=en|access-date=2020-08-06|archive-date=2017-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170906071716/http://www.santander.com/csgs/Satellite/CFWCSancomQP01/en_GB/Corporate/Investor-Relations/Ms-Ana-Botin-Sanz-de-Sautuola-y-OShea.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>她是柏廷家族的第四代成员。在此之前，她曾担任桑坦德英国公司的首席执行官，从2010年12月起一直到接任执行主席為止。

2013年2月，她在[[BBC廣播四台|BBC廣播四台]]的《Woman's Hour》节目中位列英国第三大有影响力的女人。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b007qlvb/features/power-list-100|title=BBC Radio 4 - Woman's Hour - The Power List 2013|work=BBC|access-date=2020-08-06|archive-date=2013-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130215063524/http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b007qlvb/features/power-list-100|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 早年生活 ==
柏廷的父亲是西班牙银行家{{tsl|en|Emilio Botín||埃米利奥·柏廷}}，埃米利奥曾是[[桑坦德銀行|桑坦德銀行]]的执行主席，母亲是钢琴家[[帕洛玛·奥谢|帕洛玛·奥谢]]。她在{{tsl|en|St Mary's School, Ascot||St Mary's School, Ascot}}接受了高中教育。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ft.com/content/7c182ab8-9c33-11e4-b9f8-00144feabdc0|title=London: Sexism and the City|first1=Harriet|last1=Agnew|first2=Patrick|last2=Jenkins|date=2015-01-16|website=Financial Times|accessdate=2018-03-20|archive-date=2018-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180620153120/https://www.ft.com/content/7c182ab8-9c33-11e4-b9f8-00144feabdc0|dead-url=no}}</ref>然后在[[布林莫爾學院|布林莫爾學院]]学习经济学。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.abc.es/economia/20140915/abci-ana-botin-perfil-201409142239.html|title=Ana Botín, la discreta sombra de su padre|last=Pérez|first=María Jesús|date=2014-09-15|work=ABC.es|access-date=2018-06-20|language=es|trans-title=Ana Botín, the discreet shadow of her father|archive-date=2018-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180823210609/https://www.abc.es/economia/20140915/abci-ana-botin-perfil-201409142239.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==职业生涯==
1980到1988年柏廷在美国[[摩根大通|摩根大通]]工作。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.worldfinance.com/banking/ana-botin-the-most-powerful-woman-in-finance|title=Ana Botín: the most powerful woman in finance|website=www.worldfinance.com|language=en-US|access-date=2020-02-20|archive-date=2021-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107142836/https://www.worldfinance.com/banking/ana-botin-the-most-powerful-woman-in-finance|dead-url=no}}</ref>1988年，她回到西班牙，开始为桑坦德集团工作。2002年，她成为西班牙银行{{tsl|en|Banesto||Banesto}}的执行主席。2010年11月，柏廷接替{{tsl|en|António Mota de Sousa Horta Osório||安东尼奥·奥尔塔·奥索里奥}}担任桑坦德英国公司首席执行官。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://dealbook.nytimes.com/2010/11/04/ana-patricia-botin-to-head-santander-uk/|title=Ana Patricia Botin to Head Santander UK|publisher=New York Times|accessdate=2013-01-10|date=2010-11-04|archive-date=2018-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180630105827/https://dealbook.nytimes.com/2010/11/04/ana-patricia-botin-to-head-santander-uk/|dead-url=no}}</ref>    

2013年，她被任命为[[可口可乐公司|可口可乐公司]]董事。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vcstar.com/news/2013/jul/18/coca-cola-board-elects-ana-botin-as-a-director/|title=Coca-Cola board elects Ana Botin as a director|publisher=|accessdate=2018-01-04|archive-date=2020-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200517163254/http://www.vcstar.com/errors/404/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2014年9月，她被任命为[[桑坦德銀行|桑坦德銀行]]主席。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.santander.com/csgs/Satellite/CFWCSancomQP01/en_GB/Corporate/Press-Room/2014/09/10/Ana-Botin-unanimously-appointed-to-chair-the-board-of-Banco-Santander-.html|title=Ana Botín, unanimously appointed to chair the board of Banco Santander|publisher=|access-date=2020-08-06|archive-date=2016-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161111013903/http://www.santander.com/csgs/Satellite/CFWCSancomQP01/en_GB/Corporate/Press-Room/2014/09/10/Ana-Botin-unanimously-appointed-to-chair-the-board-of-Banco-Santander-.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>她是柏廷家族的第四代成员。<ref name=Telegraph>{{cite news|title=Emilio Botín - obituary|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/obituaries/11095293/Emilio-Botin-obituary.html|accessdate=2015-08-04|work=Daily Telegraph|date=2014-09-14|archive-date=2018-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180622233841/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/obituaries/11095293/Emilio-Botin-obituary.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==个人生活==
1983年，她嫁给了第九代Borghetto侯爵之子，银行家Guillermo Morenés y Mariátegui。<ref name=ElMundo>{{cite news|last1=Ruiz|first1=Borja|title=Guillermo Morenés, el consorte de la nueva primera dama de la banca|url=http://www.elmundo.es/loc/2014/09/13/54133b4cca47410a028b4571.html|accessdate=2015-08-04|work=El Mundo|date=2014-09-13|archive-date=2015-10-07|archive-url=https://archive.is/20151007231753/http://www.elmundo.es/loc/2014/09/13/54133b4cca47410a028b4571.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>他们有三个孩子。

2010年，她的丈夫在伦敦[[贝尔格莱维亚|贝尔格莱维亚]]买了一套六居室的房子。<ref name=Bloomberg_02>{{cite news|last1=Penty|first1=Charles|title=Banking Queen Botin Plans U.K. IPO in Santander Succession Test|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2011-03-08/banking-queen-botin-plans-u-k-ipo-seen-determining-santander-succession|accessdate=2015-08-04|work=Bloomberg|date=2011-03-08|archive-date=2018-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180322015549/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2011-03-08/banking-queen-botin-plans-u-k-ipo-seen-determining-santander-succession|dead-url=no}}</ref>他们还在瑞士滑雪胜地{{tsl|en|Gstaad||格斯塔德}}拥有一所房产。<ref name=ElMundo />

2015年12月，她将被授予[[大英帝國勳章|大英帝國勳章]]（DBE），以表彰其对英国金融业的贡献。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Trotman|first1=Andrew|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/newsbysector/banksandfinance/12038346/Santander-boss-Ana-Botin-awarded-honorary-damehood.html|title=Santander boss Ana Botin awarded honorary damehood|accessdate=2015-12-25|work=[[每日电讯报|The Daily Telegraph.]]|date=2015-12-08|archive-date=2018-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180322151541/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/newsbysector/banksandfinance/12038346/Santander-boss-Ana-Botin-awarded-honorary-damehood.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

同年，柏廷获得了FIRST负责任资本主义奖。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://twitter.com/simonmanleyfco/status/677628366414094336|title=Ana Botín, of @bancosantander receives the FIRST award for Responsible Capitalism 2015 from @sajidjavid in Londonpic.twitter.com/Dku5DijzrR|first=Simon|last=Manley|date=2015-12-17|access-date=2020-08-06|archive-date=2017-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170521132808/https://twitter.com/simonmanleyfco/status/677628366414094336|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://responsible-capitalism.org/2016/01/2015/|title=2015 Award|first=Harry|last=Dobbs|date=2016-01-08|website=Responsible Capitalism|access-date=2020-08-06|archive-date=2020-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201203165114/https://responsible-capitalism.org/2016/01/2015/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 奖项和荣誉 ==
2005年柏廷首次入选《[[福布斯|福布斯]]》[[世界百名权威女性|世界百名权威女性]]排行榜<ref>{{cite news|title=#99 Ana Patricia Botín|work=forbes.com|url=https://www.forbes.com/lists/2005/11/L2WX.html|accessdate=2008-07-09|archive-date=2018-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180322022010/https://www.forbes.com/lists/2005/11/L2WX.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2019年排名该榜单第八位。<ref>{{Cite web|title=The World's Most Powerful Women 2019|url=https://www.forbes.com/power-women/|access-date=2020-03-06|website=Forbes|language=en|archive-date=2014-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140628182127/http://www.forbes.com/power-women/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

